Our Company
At Ocwen, our mission is to delight our customers through caring service and innovative home-ownership solutions. 
We offer loan investors (our servicing clients) a variety of tailor-made servicing, sub-servicing, special servicing and stand-by servicing solutions for both residential and commercial loans and REO.  Our servicing clients include private label residential mortgage-backed securities (RMBS) trusts and some of the largest financial institutions in the U.S., including Fannie Mae, Freddie Mac and Ginnie Mae.  Our servicing portfolio consists of purchased mortgage servicing assets, subservicing and servicing of loans we originate.
We are a leader in the servicing industry in foreclosure prevention and loss mitigation which helps families stay in their homes and improves financial outcomes for loan investors.  Our leadership in the industry is evidenced by our high cure rate for delinquent loans and above average rate of continuing performance by homeowners whose loans we service.  Ocwen has provided more loan modifications under the Federal Government’s Home Affordable Modification Program (HAMP) than any other mortgage servicer.  Through our outstanding staff and community outreach efforts, we have been widely recognized in the national media and by consumer advocacy groups as an industry leader in responsible home retention solutions.  These outreach efforts help our customers save money, build equity and, most importantly, stay in their homes.  At every turn, we strive to delight homeowners through caring service and innovative homeownership solutions.
We also offer and originate residential mortgage loans through our Homeward Residential subsidiary and reverse mortgages through our Liberty Home Equity Solutions subsidiary.  Through our personalized, technology-driven systems, we are committed to providing homeowners, including senior homeowners, with superior solutions and the highest level of customer service.  Please visit www.homewardfunding.com and www.libertyreversemortgage.com for more information.  
Ocwen Financial Corporation is a financial services holding company which, through its subsidiaries, originates and services loans.  We are headquartered in West Palm Beach, Florida, with offices throughout the United States, the U.S. Virgin Islands and support operations in India and the Philippines.  We have been serving our customers since 1988.


